Quickstrike:




"Why ya on th' beach?" Quickstrike said into his comm-link. "Ah could use ya 
t' keep watch wit' me." He heard Stingtra, and replied, "Ah don't know where 
one is, ah jus' want ya t' find one an' bring it back here. Ya don't need 
nothin' t' do it, just turn it on stand-by ah reckon, then bring it back t' 
base as fast as ya can. Go searchin' fer one with someone if ya want. Who's 
out there wit' ya?"
